### Order Management API — sample requests
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension or the JetBrains/VS HTTP client.

@host = http://localhost:5216

### Health check (implemented)
GET {{host}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Swagger / OpenAPI document (implemented)
GET {{host}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json


### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Planned endpoints (Phase 2 — not implemented yet).
### Listed here so the contract is visible; they will return 404 until implemented.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Run document synchronisation
# POST {{host}}/api/sync/documents

### Get documents for an order
# GET {{host}}/api/orders/ORD-001/documents

### Get synchronisation history
# GET {{host}}/api/sync/logs

### Re-send the latest sync log to Google Sheets
# POST {{host}}/api/sync/logs/latest/send-to-google
